  "description": "<p>A physical sign of corruption is a noticeable change to your character’s body that can range from subtle to glaringly obvious. Many of these signs can be rationalized by others as existing naturally but are nevertheless found to be strange or off-putting by the every day Ironlander. While it is true that your character could have the condition maimed marked on their character sheet from corruption, I left that off the list below.</p>",
